What does IDE stand for?
Interface Development Environment
Integrated Development Environment
Interface Developed Extension
None of the above

Which of the following statements is not correct
Python is mostly used in data analytics
HTML and JavaScript are good for front-end web development
Dart is best known for mobile applications
SQL is used for styling front-end interfaces
SQL is used for styling front-end interfaces is not correct. SQL is a language used in working with databases and has nothing to do with front-end styling.
